<title type="html"><![CDATA[New directory structure for WIki pages]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4540&amp;p=39618#p39618"><![CDATA[
I've changed the page structure for the <a href="http://nesdevwiki.org" class="postlink">wiki</a> to be a little cleaner.<br /><br />Instead of pages being at nesdevwiki.org/index.php/Foo, they will be at nesdevwiki.org/wiki/Foo. This matches the Wikipedia structure, and will be a little nicer to link or type.<br /><br />I left a redirect for the old structure, so existing links should still work. Let me know if you find anything broken, or find some old links that don't work anymore.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=134">atarimike</a> — Wed Nov 05, 2008 2:19 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
